<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Patch>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Glass+Lights</li>
      <li>Just Glass</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="WindowReinforced_TMaterialsGlass"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>강화 유리 창문</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="AutoDoorGlassTempered_TMaterials"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>강화 유리 자동문</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="AutoDoorGlassTempered_TMaterials"]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>방을 나눕니다. 자동이기 때문에 사람들이 속도를 줄이지 않고 문을 통해 이동할 수 있게 합니다. 빛이 통과할 수 있도록 합니다.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="DoorGlassTempered_TMaterials"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>강화 유리 문</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="DoorGlassTempered_TMaterials"]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>방을 나눕니다. 빛이 통과할 수 있도록 합니다.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
      </operations>
    </match>
  </Operation>
</Patch>